      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Esecuzione per fine 2. livello di rottura       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-prn-flg-int    not  = spaces
                     go to prn-rou-pri-821.
           perform   prn-fin-lr2-000      thru prn-fin-lr2-999        .
       prn-rou-pri-821.
           exit.
